snippet.title: Osu tatakae ouendan 2005 (DS) - Full Playthrough
snippet.description:

The Osu! Tatakae! Ouendan series was developed by iNiS Corporation exclusively for the Nintendo DS system and published by Nintendo. It consists of the Japan-exclusive Osu! Tatakae! Ouendan duology and its international counterpart, Elite Beat Agents, which contains the same gameplay but had its characters and themes adapted to fit a Western audience.

Moero! Nekketsu Rhythm Damashii Osu! Tatakae! Ouendan 2 - https://youtu.be/SNxsnfxFrFI

Osu! Tatakae! Ouendan  - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Osu!_Tatakae!_Ouendan

Act 1
1. Asian Kung-Fu Generation – "Loop & Loop" 01:24

Act 2
2. Ulfuls – "Guts da ze!! 05:53
3. 175R – "Melody" 09:52
4. Morning Musume – "Koi no Dance Site" 13:52

Act 3
5. Tomoyasu Hotei – "Thrill" 18:17
6. nobodyknows+ – "Kokoro Odoru" 22:25
7. B'z – "Atsuki Kodō no Hate" 26:45
8. The Blue Hearts – "Linda Linda" 30:28

Act 4
9. Road of Major – "Taisetsu na Mono" 35:07
10. Kishidan – "One Night Carnival" 39:31
11.Linda Yamamoto – "Neraiuchi" 43:51

Act 5
12. Hitomi Yaida – "Over The Distance" (by Ayako Kawajima) 48:41

Act 6
13. The Yellow Monkey – "Taiyō ga Moeteiru"  53:07
14. Orange Range – "Shanghai Honey" 57:33

Act 7
15. L'Arc-en-Ciel – "Ready Steady Go" 01:02:26
